untuk acara spesial.

455
00:50:42,667 --> 00:50:44,747
<i>Perhitungan rasio ukuran</i>

456
00:50:44,771 --> 00:50:46,907
<i>Tinggi 39.7 cm.
Lebar 67.5 cm.</i>

457
00:51:00,708 --> 00:51:02,168
