505
00:55:40,708 --> 00:55:44,208
- Maria, ayo.
- Masuk ke dalam.

506
00:55:52,417 --> 00:55:54,677
Jostein, kau harus lupakan itu.
Ayo, ayo.

507
00:56:24,000 --> 00:56:25,820
<i>Alarm jangkar.</i>

508
00:56:29,833 --> 00:56:31,473
<i>Alarm jangkar.</i>

